unittitle_ssm: Zan Gibbs Riot Grrrl Zine Collection
abstract_ssm: The Zan Gibbs Riot Grrrl Zine collection consists of zines collected by Gibbs while she was involved in the Riot Grrrl movement in the early to mid-1990s, in Washington, DC, Vancouver, BC, and Portland, Oregon. While living in Vancouver, Gibbs started the Canadian version of Riot Grrrl Press, distributing zines through the mail throughout Canada.
